#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="an7.29"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an7.29:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 7 "
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 7 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an7.29:0.2"
msgid "3. Vajjisattakavagga "
msgstr "3. The Vajji Seven "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
#. VAR: 29. Dutiyaparihānisutta → upāsakaaparibhāgiyasuttaṃ (bj)
msgctxt "an7.29:0.3"
msgid "29. Dutiyaparihānisutta "
msgstr "29. Non-decline for a Lay Follower "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "an7.29:1.1"
msgid "“Sattime, bhikkhave, dhammā upāsakassa parihānāya saṃvattanti. "
msgstr "“These seven things lead to the decline of a lay follower. "

msgctxt "an7.29:1.2"
msgid "Katame satta? "
msgstr "What seven? "

msgctxt "an7.29:1.3"
msgid "Bhikkhudassanaṃ hāpeti, "
msgstr "They stop seeing the mendicants. "

msgctxt "an7.29:1.4"
msgid "saddhammassavanaṃ pamajjati, "
msgstr "They neglect listening to the true teaching. "

msgctxt "an7.29:1.5"
msgid "adhisīle na sikkhati, "
msgstr "They don’t train in higher ethical conduct. "

msgctxt "an7.29:1.6"
msgid "appasādabahulo hoti, "
msgstr "They’re very suspicious about mendicants, whether senior, junior, or middle. "

msgctxt "an7.29:1.7"
msgid "bhikkhūsu theresu ceva navesu ca majjhimesu ca upārambhacitto dhammaṃ suṇāti randhagavesī, "
msgstr "They listen to the teaching with a hostile, fault-finding mind. "

msgctxt "an7.29:1.8"
msgid "ito bahiddhā dakkhiṇeyyaṃ gavesati, "
msgstr "They seek outside of the Buddhist community for those worthy of religious donations. "

msgctxt "an7.29:1.9"
msgid "tattha ca pubbakāraṃ karoti. "
msgstr "And they serve them first. "

msgctxt "an7.29:1.10"
msgid "Ime kho, bhikkhave, satta dhammā upāsakassa parihānāya saṃvattanti. "
msgstr "These seven things lead to the decline of a lay follower. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "an7.29:2.1"
msgid "Sattime, bhikkhave, dhammā upāsakassa aparihānāya saṃvattanti. "
msgstr "These seven things don’t lead to the decline of a lay follower. "

msgctxt "an7.29:2.2"
msgid "Katame satta? "
msgstr "What seven? "

msgctxt "an7.29:2.3"
msgid "Bhikkhudassanaṃ na hāpeti, "
msgstr "They don’t stop seeing the mendicants. "

msgctxt "an7.29:2.4"
msgid "saddhammassavanaṃ nappamajjati, "
msgstr "They don’t neglect listening to the true teaching. "

msgctxt "an7.29:2.5"
msgid "adhisīle sikkhati, "
msgstr "They train in higher ethical conduct. "

msgctxt "an7.29:2.6"
msgid "pasādabahulo hoti, "
msgstr "They’re very confident about mendicants, whether senior, junior, or middle. "

msgctxt "an7.29:2.7"
msgid "bhikkhūsu theresu ceva navesu ca majjhimesu ca anupārambhacitto dhammaṃ suṇāti na randhagavesī, "
msgstr "They don’t listen to the teaching with a hostile, fault-finding mind. "

msgctxt "an7.29:2.8"
msgid "na ito bahiddhā dakkhiṇeyyaṃ gavesati, "
msgstr "They don’t seek outside of the Buddhist community for those worthy of religious donations. "

msgctxt "an7.29:2.9"
msgid "idha ca pubbakāraṃ karoti. "
msgstr "And they serve the Buddhist community first. "

msgctxt "an7.29:2.10"
msgid "Ime kho, bhikkhave, satta dhammā upāsakassa aparihānāya saṃvattantī”ti. "
msgstr "These seven things don’t lead to the decline of a lay follower.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an7.29:2.11"
msgid "Idamavoca bhagavā. "
msgstr "That is what the Buddha said. "

msgctxt "an7.29:2.12"
msgid "Idaṃ vatvāna sugato athāparaṃ etadavoca satthā: "
msgstr "Then the Holy One, the Teacher, went on to say: "

#. HTML: </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli4.26, sc3
msgctxt "an7.29:3.1"
msgid "“Dassanaṃ bhāvitattānaṃ, "
msgstr "“A lay follower stops seeing "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an7.29:3.2"
msgid "Yo hāpeti upāsako; "
msgstr "those who have developed themselves "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an7.29:3.3"
msgid "Savanañca ariyadhammānaṃ, "
msgstr "and listening to the teaching of the noble ones. "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an7.29:3.4"
msgid "Adhisīle na sikkhati. "
msgstr "They don’t train in higher ethical conduct, "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc4
msgctxt "an7.29:4.1"
msgid "Appasādo ca bhikkhūsu, "
msgstr "and their suspicion about mendicants "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an7.29:4.2"
msgid "bhiyyo bhiyyo pavaḍḍhati; "
msgstr "just grows and grows. "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an7.29:4.3"
msgid "Upārambhakacitto ca, "
msgstr "They want to listen to the true teaching "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an7.29:4.4"
msgid "saddhammaṃ sotumicchati. "
msgstr "with a fault-finding mind. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc5
msgctxt "an7.29:5.1"
msgid "Ito ca bahiddhā aññaṃ, "
msgstr "They seek outside the Buddhist community "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an7.29:5.2"
msgid "dakkhiṇeyyaṃ gavesati; "
msgstr "for someone else worthy of religious donations, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an7.29:5.3"
msgid "Tattheva ca pubbakāraṃ, "
msgstr "and that lay follower "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an7.29:5.4"
msgid "yo karoti upāsako. "
msgstr "serves them first. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc6
msgctxt "an7.29:6.1"
msgid "Ete kho parihāniye, "
msgstr "These seven principles leading to decline "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an7.29:6.2"
msgid "satta dhamme sudesite; "
msgstr "have been well taught. "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an7.29:6.3"
msgid "Upāsako sevamāno, "
msgstr "A lay follower who practices them "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an7.29:6.4"
msgid "saddhammā parihāyati. "
msgstr "falls away from the true teaching. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc7
msgctxt "an7.29:7.1"
msgid "Dassanaṃ bhāvitattānaṃ, "
msgstr "A lay follower doesn’t stop seeing "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an7.29:7.2"
msgid "Yo na hāpeti upāsako; "
msgstr "those who have developed themselves "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an7.29:7.3"
msgid "Savanañca ariyadhammānaṃ, "
msgstr "and listening to the teaching of the noble ones. "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an7.29:7.4"
msgid "Adhisīle ca sikkhati. "
msgstr "They train in higher ethical conduct, "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc8
msgctxt "an7.29:8.1"
msgid "Pasādo cassa bhikkhūsu, "
msgstr "and their confidence in mendicants "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an7.29:8.2"
msgid "bhiyyo bhiyyo pavaḍḍhati; "
msgstr "just grows and grows. "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an7.29:8.3"
msgid "Anupārambhacitto ca, "
msgstr "They want to listen to the true teaching "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an7.29:8.4"
msgid "saddhammaṃ sotumicchati. "
msgstr "without a fault-finding mind. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc9
msgctxt "an7.29:9.1"
msgid "Na ito bahiddhā aññaṃ, "
msgstr "They don’t seek outside the Buddhist community "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an7.29:9.2"
msgid "dakkhiṇeyyaṃ gavesati; "
msgstr "for someone else worthy of religious donations, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an7.29:9.3"
msgid "Idheva ca pubbakāraṃ, "
msgstr "and that lay follower "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an7.29:9.4"
msgid "yo karoti upāsako. "
msgstr "serves the Buddhist community first. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc10
msgctxt "an7.29:10.1"
msgid "Ete kho aparihāniye, "
msgstr "These seven principles that prevent decline "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an7.29:10.2"
msgid "Satta dhamme sudesite; "
msgstr "have been well taught. "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an7.29:10.3"
msgid "Upāsako sevamāno, "
msgstr "A lay follower who practices them "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an7.29:10.4"
msgid "Saddhammā na parihāyatī”ti. "
msgstr "doesn’t fall away from the true teaching.” "

#. HTML: </p></blockquote><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an7.29:10.5"
msgid "Navamaṃ. "
msgstr ""

#. HTML: </p></article></section></body></html>
